{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1162,"text":"When I was young,\nI prided myself as a nonconformist"},{"time":5704,"text":"in the conservative\nU.S. state I live in, Kansas."},{"time":10429,"text":"I didn't follow along with the crowd."},{"time":12742,"text":"I wasn't afraid to try\nweird clothing trends or hairstyles."},{"time":16173,"text":"I was outspoken and extremely social."},{"time":19762,"text":"Even these pictures and postcards \nof my London semester abroad 16 years ago"},{"time":26093,"text":"show that I obviously didn't care\nif I was perceived as weird or different."},{"time":32097,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34681,"text":"But that same year \nI was in London, 16 years ago,"},{"time":39290,"text":"I realized something about myself\nthat actually was somewhat unique,"},{"time":44699,"text":"and that changed everything."},{"time":49169,"text":"I became the opposite\nof who I thought I once was."},{"time":53079,"text":"I stayed in my room\ninstead of socializing."},{"time":56005,"text":"I stopped engaging in clubs\nand leadership activities."},{"time":60385,"text":"I didn't want to stand out\nin the crowd anymore."},{"time":64260,"text":"I told myself it was because\nI was growing up and maturing,"},{"time":68325,"text":"not that I was suddenly\nlooking for acceptance."},{"time":71559,"text":"I had always assumed I was immune\nto needing acceptance."},{"time":74580,"text":"After all, I was a bit unconventional."},{"time":77814,"text":"But I realize now"},{"time":79351,"text":"that the moment I realized\nsomething was different about me"},{"time":83516,"text":"was the exact same moment\nthat I began conforming and hiding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89728,"text":"Hiding is a progressive habit,"},{"time":92200,"text":"and once you start hiding,"},{"time":93948,"text":"it becomes harder and harder\nto step forward and speak out."},{"time":99888,"text":"In fact, even now,"},{"time":101822,"text":"when I was talking to people\nabout what this talk was about,"},{"time":105697,"text":"I made up a cover story"},{"time":107533,"text":"and I even hid the truth\nabout my TED Talk."},{"time":112388,"text":"So it is fitting and scary"},{"time":117329,"text":"that I have returned \nto this city 16 years later"},{"time":121519,"text":"and I have chosen this stage\nto finally stop hiding."},{"time":128093,"text":"What have I been hiding\nfor 16 years?"},{"time":134205,"text":"I am a lesbian."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137602,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153513,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156038,"text":"I've struggled to say those words,"},{"time":158397,"text":"because I didn't want\nto be defined by them."},{"time":161573,"text":"Every time I would think\nabout coming out in the past,"},{"time":164202,"text":"I would think to myself,\nbut I just want to be known as Morgana,"},{"time":169266,"text":"uniquely Morgana,"},{"time":171430,"text":"but not \"my lesbian friend Morgana,\"\nor \"my gay coworker Morgana.\""},{"time":176439,"text":"Just Morgana."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178893,"text":"For those of you from large\nmetropolitan areas,"},{"time":182302,"text":"this may not seem like a big deal to you."},{"time":184895,"text":"It may seem strange \nthat I have suppressed the truth"},{"time":187839,"text":"and hidden this for so long."},{"time":191035,"text":"But I was paralyzed by my fear\nof not being accepted."},{"time":196818,"text":"And I'm not alone, of course."},{"time":199459,"text":"A 2013 Deloitte study found\nthat a surprisingly large number of people"},{"time":204308,"text":"hide aspects of their identity."},{"time":207078,"text":"Of all the employees they surveyed,"},{"time":209949,"text":"61 percent reported changing an aspect\nof their behavior or their appearance"},{"time":215568,"text":"in order to fit in at work."},{"time":217841,"text":"Of all the gay, lesbian\nand bisexual employees,"},{"time":222470,"text":"83 percent admitted to changing\nsome aspects of themselves"},{"time":227260,"text":"so they would not \nappear at work \"too gay.\""},{"time":232417,"text":"The study found that even in companies"},{"time":235340,"text":"with diversity policies\nand inclusion programs,"},{"time":239253,"text":"employees struggle\nto be themselves at work"},{"time":242006,"text":"because they believe \nconformity is critical"},{"time":244989,"text":"to their long-term career advancement."},{"time":248496,"text":"And while I was surprised\nthat so many people just like me"},{"time":253438,"text":"waste so much energy\ntrying to hide themselves,"},{"time":257231,"text":"I was scared when I discovered\nthat my silence"},{"time":261122,"text":"has life-or-death consequences\nand long-term social repercussions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269117,"text":"Twelve years:"},{"time":271308,"text":"the length by which \nlife expectancy is shortened"},{"time":274979,"text":"for gay, lesbian and bisexual people\nin highly anti-gay communities"},{"time":281017,"text":"compared to accepting communities."},{"time":284603,"text":"Twelve years reduced life expectancy."},{"time":289301,"text":"When I read that in The Advocate \nmagazine this year,"},{"time":292429,"text":"I realized I could no longer\nafford to keep silent."},{"time":296904,"text":"The effects of personal stress and\nsocial stigmas are a deadly combination."},{"time":304692,"text":"The study found that gays\nin anti-gay communities"},{"time":307963,"text":"had higher rates of heart disease,\nviolence and suicide."},{"time":313710,"text":"What I once thought\nwas simply a personal matter"},{"time":317040,"text":"I realized had a ripple effect"},{"time":319226,"text":"that went into the workplace\nand out into the community"},{"time":321820,"text":"for every story just like mine."},{"time":325185,"text":"My choice to hide\nand not share who I really am"},{"time":329005,"text":"may have inadvertently contributed\nto this exact same environment"},{"time":333048,"text":"and atmosphere of discrimination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336192,"text":"I'd always told myself\nthere's no reason to share that I was gay,"},{"time":341592,"text":"but the idea that my silence\nhas social consequences"},{"time":345809,"text":"was really driven home this year\nwhen I missed an opportunity"},{"time":350669,"text":"to change the atmosphere of discrimination\nin my own home state of Kansas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356421,"text":"In February, the Kansas House of \nRepresentatives brought up a bill for vote"},{"time":361623,"text":"that would have essentially\nallowed businesses"},{"time":364147,"text":"to use religious freedom as a reason\nto deny gays services."},{"time":373063,"text":"A former coworker and friend of mine"},{"time":376245,"text":"has a father who serves\nin the Kansas House of Representatives."},{"time":381068,"text":"He voted in favor of the bill,"},{"time":386253,"text":"in favor of a law that would allow \nbusinesses to not serve me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394647,"text":"How does my friend feel"},{"time":396436,"text":"about lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender,\nqueer and questioning people?"},{"time":401922,"text":"How does her father feel?"},{"time":404611,"text":"I don't know, because I was never honest \nwith them about who I am."},{"time":410499,"text":"And that shakes me to the core."},{"time":413773,"text":"What if I had told her my story years ago?"},{"time":417204,"text":"Could she have told \nher father my experience?"},{"time":419853,"text":"Could I have ultimately\nhelped change his vote?"},{"time":424885,"text":"I will never know,"},{"time":427348,"text":"and that made me realize\nI had done nothing"},{"time":431480,"text":"to try to make a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435053,"text":"How ironic that I work\nin human resources,"},{"time":439074,"text":"a profession that works to welcome,"},{"time":441512,"text":"connect and encourage\nthe development of employees,"},{"time":445097,"text":"a profession that advocates\nthat the diversity of society"},{"time":448339,"text":"should be reflected in the workplace,"},{"time":451004,"text":"and yet I have done nothing\nto advocate for diversity."},{"time":456779,"text":"When I came to this company one year ago,"},{"time":459649,"text":"I thought to myself, this company \nhas anti-discrimination policies"},{"time":464724,"text":"that protect gay, lesbian,\nbisexual and transgender people."},{"time":468777,"text":"Their commitment to diversity is evident\nthrough their global inclusion programs."},{"time":474483,"text":"When I walk through the doors\nof this company, I will finally come out."},{"time":480551,"text":"But I didn't."},{"time":482540,"text":"Instead of taking advantage\nof the opportunity,"},{"time":486250,"text":"I did nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499838,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":507737,"text":"When I was looking through\nmy London journal and scrapbook"},{"time":511652,"text":"from my London semester\nabroad 16 years ago,"},{"time":514902,"text":"I came across this modified quote\nfrom Toni Morrison's book, \"Paradise.\""},{"time":521547,"text":"\"There are more scary things\ninside than outside.\""},{"time":525841,"text":"And then I wrote a note\nto myself at the bottom:"},{"time":529099,"text":"\"Remember this.\""},{"time":531983,"text":"I'm sure I was trying to encourage myself\nto get out and explore London,"},{"time":536685,"text":"but the message I missed was the need \nto start exploring and embracing myself."},{"time":543762,"text":"What I didn't realize\nuntil all these years later"},{"time":547465,"text":"is that the biggest obstacles\nI will ever have to overcome"},{"time":552371,"text":"are my own fears and insecurities."},{"time":556438,"text":"I believe that by facing my fears inside,\nI will be able to change reality outside."},{"time":565498,"text":"I made a choice today"},{"time":567791,"text":"to reveal a part of myself\nthat I have hidden for too long."},{"time":574333,"text":"I hope that this means\nI will never hide again,"},{"time":578644,"text":"and I hope that by coming out today,\nI can do something to change the data"},{"time":585492,"text":"and also to help others who feel different\nbe more themselves and more fulfilled"},{"time":591903,"text":"in both their professional\nand personal lives."},{"time":596394,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":599147,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}